trans-unit.source: Contains the properties of a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult" /> instance.
<xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult> instances are similar to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> instances.

The notable difference is that the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> retrieves its information from the Active Directory Domain Services hierarchy each time a new object is accessed, whereas the data for the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult> is already available in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResultCollection> that a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher> query returns.
trans-unit.target: 주목할 만한 차이점은는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> 해당 정보를 검색에서 Active Directory 도메인 서비스 계층 될 때마다 새 개체에 액세스 하는 반면에 대 한 데이터는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult> 에 이미 있지 않은지는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResultCollection> 하는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher>쿼리에서 반환 합니다.

trans-unit.source: If you try to get a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult> property that your query did not specify for retrieval, the property will not be available.
trans-unit.target: 가져오려는 경우는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult> 검색에 대 한 쿼리를 지정 하지 않은 속성을 속성은 사용할 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The name of the property to find.
Determines whether the property that has the specified name belongs to this collection.
The return value is <see langword="true" /> if the specified property belongs to this collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
An array of type <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ResultPropertyValueCollection" /> that receives this collection's properties.
The zero-based array index at which to begin copying the properties.
Copies the properties from this collection to an array, starting at a particular index of the array.
The name of the property to retrieve.
Gets the property from this collection that has the specified name.
A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ResultPropertyValueCollection" /> that has the specified name.
In C#, this property is the indexer for the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ResultPropertyValueCollection> class.
In JScript, you can use the default indexed properties defined by a type, but you cannot explicitly define your own.
trans-unit.target: Jscript에서는 형식에 의해 정의 된 기본 인덱싱된 속성을 사용할 수 있습니다 하지만 정의할 수는 없습니다 명시적으로 직접.

trans-unit.source: However, specifying the expando attribute on a class automatically provides a default indexed property whose type is Object and whose index type is <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: 하지만 자동으로 클래스에 expando 특성을 지정 하는 제공 형식의 개체가 고 인덱스 형식이 기본 인덱싱된 속성이 <xref:System.String>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the names of the properties in this collection.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> that contains the names of the properties in this collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> 이 컬렉션에 있는 속성의 이름이 들어 있는입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the values of the properties in this collection.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> that contains the values of the properties in this collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> 이 컬렉션에 있는 속성의 값이 들어 있는입니다.
